Ki-tok-tou5 teh kiaN5 kong-gi7, u7 kong-gi7 e5 seng-oah8. ¡§KiN3-na7 toa3 ti7 I e5, bo5 hoan7 choe7; kiN3-na7 hoan7 choe7 e5, be7-bat khoaN3-kiN3 I, ia7 m7-bat I,......Hoan7 choe7 e5 si7 tui3 Mou5-kui2 chhut,......KiN3-na7 tui3 Siong7-te3 siN e5 chiu7 bo5 hoan7 choe7, in-ui7 I e5 cheng2 tng5-tng5 tiam3-ti7 i; i ia7 boe7 hoan7 choe7, in-ui7 i si7 tui3 Siong7-te3 siN e5. Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5 kap Mou5-kui2 e5 kiaN2-ji5 tui3 an2-ni hian2-beng5¡¨ (I Iok-han7 3:6, 8~10). Ti7 i2-siong7 chiah-e5 Seng3-keng-chat lai7-bin7 e5 tong7-su5, long2 si7 hian7-chai7 chin3-heng5 sek, bo5 koh soa3-chiap hoan7 choe7 a2-si7 ke3-siok8 teh hoan7-choe7. Choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5 bo5 koh ke3-siok8 hoan7 choe7, in-ui7 i bo5 tiam3-ti7 choe7-ok e5 lai7-bin7; chiu7-si7 Ki-tok-tou5 bo5 koh ke3-siok8 ti7 choe7-ok e5 lai7-bin7 hong3-chhiong3, ke3-siok8 hoan7 choe7. Che m7 si7 i seng-oah8 e5 tek8-tiong5, oaN7 oe7 lai5 kong2, i bo5 koh-chai3 tit8-tit8 hoan7 choe7. I na7-si7 koh-chai3 ke3-siok8 tit8-tit8 hoan7 choe7, chiu7 m7 si7 tui3 Siong7-te3 siN e5, i iu5-goan5 siok8 ti7 Sat-tan.
2.Chong2-si7 I Oe7 Poah8-to2 Ham7-loh8 Choe7-ok
¡§Goa2 e5 soe3-kiaN2 ah, goa2 sia2 chiah-e5 hou7 lin2, si7 beh hou7 lin2 bo5 hoan7 choe7. Na7 u7 lang5 hoan7 choe7, chiu7 ti7 Pe7 e5 bin7-cheng5 lan2 u7 Po2-hui7-su, chiu7-si7 gi7-lang5 Ia5-sou Ki-tok; I ui7-tioh8 lan2 e5 choe7, choe3 ban2-hoe5 e5 che3¡¨ (I Iok-han7 2:1~2). Ti7 chia kong2 chin beng5, Ki-tok-tou5 m7-bian2 tek-khak tioh8 hoan7-choe7; i m7-bian2 kou3-i3 hoan7 choe7, a2-si7 khi3 choe3 ka-ki7 i2-keng chai e5 m7-tioh8. I tui3 choe7-ok oe7 thang tit-tioh8 thau2-pang3, m7-bian2 poah8-to2 ham7-loh8 ti7 choe7-ok.
Na7-si7, ui7-tioh8 hoan7 choe7 e5 Ki-tok-tou5, Siong7-te3 u7 chun2-pi7. Siong7-te3 kong2: ¡§Na7 u7 lang5 hoan7 choe7¡¨, ti7 chia chin beng5 ka7 lan2 kong2, Ki-tok-tou5 ia7 oe7 hoan7 choe7, Ki-tok-tou5 ia7 oe7 poah8-to2, ham7-loh8 ti7 choe7-ok. Chong2-si7 hoan7 choe7 m7 si7 chit8-e5 Ki-tok-tou5 ti7 seng-oah8 tiong cheng3-siong5 e5 piau2-hian7, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 chi2-lam5-chiam tioh8 ki2 lam5--si3, kho2-sioh ia7 oe7 siu7 pat8-mih8 e5 eng2-hiong2, chiam7-si5 oe7 ki2 pat8 hong-hiong3; chong2-si7 kau3 be2 i tek-khak oe7 koh ki2 pak--si3. Ki-tok-tou5 ia7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni, i bo5 ke3-siok8 teh hoan7 choe7, na7-si7 i kiam2-chhai2 oe7 poah8-to2 ham7-loh8 ti7 choe7-ok. I na7 hoan7 choe7, i u7 chit8-ui7 Po2-hui7-su, Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok, I chiaN5-choe3 un-tian2 e5 cho7-ui7, ban2-hoe5 e5 che3, i e5 choe7 chiu7 oe7 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2.
Chit-e5 koan-he7, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 iuN5 kap ti. Chit8-chiah iuN5 bo5 tiuN-ti5 chiu7 poah8-loh8 ti7 chit8-e5 lou7-kou5-be5 khut. Na7-si7 ti chiu7 m7 si7 an2-ni, i chit8 e7 khoaN3-tioh8 lou7-kou5-be5 khut, chiu7 tit8-tit8 chong5-khi3, chin hoaN-hi2 kam-goan7 thiau3 jip8-khi3. Kiat-ko2, chit-chiah iuN5 chiu7 koaN2-kin2 tui3 lou7-kou5-be5 khut pe5 khi2-lai5, liau2-au7, chiu7 chin7 sou2 oe7 beh li7-khui hit-e5 khut hng7-hng7; na7-si7 hit-chiah ti chiu7 bo5 siuN7 beh pe5 khi2-lai5, i ai3 tiam3-ti7 hit lai7-bin7. In-ui7 che si7 i e5 pun2-seng3, i ai3 la5-sam5 e5 lou7-kou5-be5.
