Be7 tit-kiu3 e5 lang5 , chiu7 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 hit chiah ti ai3 tiam3-ti7 lou7-kou5-be5 khut, ko7--lai5 ko7--khi3, che si7 i e5 pun2-seng3; choe7-jin5 ia7 si7 siang7-khoan2. An2-ni, li2 chiu7 oe7 thang khoaN3-chhut iuN5 kap ti pun2-seng3 e5 cheng-chha. Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5 kap Mou5-kui2 e5 kiaN2-ji5, ia7 oe7 thang tui3 an2-ni hun-piat8. In kiam2-chhai2 long2 ham7-loh8 ti7 choe7-ok e5 lai7-bin7, na7-si7 chi2-u7 chit8-e5 oe7 ke3-siok8 tiam3-ti7 choe7-ok. Ki-tok-tou5 boe7 ke3-siok8 hoan7 choe7, i bo5 ai3 tiam3-ti7 lou7-kou5-be5 khut e5 lai7-bin7. Li2 poah8-to2 hoan7-choe7, boe7 ti3-kau3 piN3-choe3 chit8-e5 bo5 sin3 e5 goa7-pang lang5 . Chong2-si7 li2 na7 iu5-goan5 tiam3-ti7 choe7-ok, chiu7 cheng3-beng5 li2 si7 chit8-e5 bo5 sin3 Siong7-te3 e5 goa7-pang lang5 .
3. Ki-tok-tou5 Na7 Hoan2 Hoe2, Siong7-te3 Boe7 Khi3-sak I.
¡§KiN3-na7 Pe7 sou2 hou7 Goa2 e5, beh long2 chiu7-kun7 Goa2; chiu7-kun7 Goa2 e5 lang5 , Goa2 koat-toan3 bo5 khi3-sak i¡¨ (Iok-han7 6:37). Siong7-te3 choat8-tui3 boe7 khi3-sak i, bo5 hou7 i choe3 I e5 kiaN2-ji5. Siong7-te3 iu5-goan5 beh khoan2-thai7 i choe3 ka-ki7 e5 kiaN2-ji5. TaN Siong7-te3 beh chaiN2-iuN7 khoan2-thai7 I e5 kiaN2-ji5? ¡§Siat-su2 i e5 kiaN2-sun pang3-sak Goa2 e5 lut8-hoat; Bo5 kiaN5 goa2 e5 hoat-tou7; Poe7-biu7 Goa2 e5 lut8-le7, Bo5 siu2 Goa2 e5 kai3-beng7; Goa2 chiu7 beh eng7 koaiN2-a2 chek-hoat8 in e5 ke3-sit; Eng7 piN chek-hoat8 in e5 choe7-ok. Chong2-si7 Goa2 tek-khak bo5 chiong Goa2 e5 chu5-ai3 it-chin7 tui3 i siu-hoe5; Iah8 tek-khak bo5 hou7 Goa2 e5 sin3-sit8 hoe3-bo5. Goa2 tek-khak bo5 sit Goa2 e5 iok; Iah8 bo5 koe2-oaN7 Goa2 e5 chhui3 sou2 kong2--e5¡¨ (Si-phian 89:30~34). Lan2 thang khoaN3 chhut Siong7-te3 beh ka3-si7 in, chek-hoat8 in, chong2-si7 tek-khak bo5 hoe3-bo5 I e5 sin3-sit8.
