¡§Goa2 beh choe3 i e5 Pe7, i beh choe3 Goa2 e5 kiaN2; i na7 hoan7-choe7, Goa2 beh eng7 lang5 e5 koaiN2, se3-kan lang5 e5 piN, chek-tok i. chong2-si7 Goa2 e5 chu5-ai3 bo5 beh li7-khui i¡¨ (II Sat-bou2-jiN2 7:14~15). Siong7-te3 si7 lan2 e5 ThiN-pe7, lan2 si7 I e5 kiaN2-ji5, lan2 na7 hoan7 choe7, I chiu7 beh ka3-si7 lan2, I beh eng7 koaiN2, eng7 piN chek-hoat8 lan2, lan2 tioh8 jim2-siu7 I e5 keng2-kai3. I e5 chu5-ai3 boe7 li7-khui lan2, lan2 iu5-goan5 si7 I e5 kiaN2-ji5.
4. Kau-poe5 U7 Toan7-choat8, Hoan2-hoe2 Chiu7 Koh Hoe5-hok8.
¡§Lan2 na7 jin7 lan2 e5 choe7, I si7 chin-sit8 kong-gi7, beh sia3-bian2 lan2 e5 choe7, soe2-tu5 lan2 long2-chong2 e5 put-gi7¡¨ (I Iok-han7 1:9). Lan2 chit8-e7 hoan7 choe7, lan2 kap Siong7-te3 e5 kau-poe5 chiu7 toan7-choat8. Lan2 na7 beh hoe5-hok8 chit-e5 kau-poe5, chiu7 tioh8 jin7-choe7 kiu5 sia3-bian2, an2-ni chiah oe7 thang kap Siong7-te3 ho5-ho2.
U7 choe7-choe7 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5, bo5 teh kap I kau-poe5, in e5 seng-oah8 bo5 sun7-than3 I, chiu7 sit-loh8 hoaN-hi2 khoai3-lok8 kap peng5-an. In-ui7 in sou2 choe3 e5, m7-si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 hoaN-hi2 e5, in u7 kou-hu7 Siong7-te3 , ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 hoan7 choe7. Chong2-si7 I iau2-ku2 teh theng3-hau7 in jin7-choe7 hoan2-hoe2; hou7 in kap Siong7-te3 e5 koan-he7 oe7 thang hoe5-hok8. Chit-e5 kau-poe5 toan7-choat8 e5 si5, lan2 e5 ki5-to2 koat-toan3 boe7 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2 chiah oe7 thang hoe5-hok8. Lan2 na7 jin7-choe7, I chiu7 chek-si5 sia3-bian2 lan2. ¡§I e5 KiaN2 Ia5-sou e5 huih soe2-tu5 lan2 long2-chong2 e5 choe7¡¨ (I Iok-han7 1:7).
