5. Ki-tok-tou5 Tioh8 Ka-ki7 Hun-piat8, Na7 Bo5, Siong7-te3 Beh Sim2-phoann3.
¡§An2-ni, hoan7-na7 chiah8 Chu2 e5 piaN2, a2-si7 lim Chu2 e5 poe, bo5 hap8-gi5 e5, si7 kou-hu7 ChU2 e5 seng-khu kap huih. Na7-si7 lang5 tioh8 ka-ki7 seng2-chhat, chiah thang chiah8 chit e5 piaN2, lim chit e5 poe. lang5 bo5 hun-piat8 Chu2 e5 seng-khu lai5 lim-chiah8, chiu7-si7 tui3 lim-chiah8 ka-ki7 chhu2 sim2-phoaN3. Sou2-i2 lin2 tiong-kan soe-lan2 e5, phoa3-piN7 e5, choe7-choe7; si2 e5 ia7 bo5 chio2. Lan2 na7 ka-ki7 sim2-mng7, chiu7 bo5 siu7 sim2-phoaN3. Chong2-si7 lan2 siu7 sim2-phoaN3, si7 hou7 Chu2 sou2 keng2-kai3, bian2-tit kap se3-kan lang5 tang5 siu7 teng7-choe7¡¨ (I Ko-lim5-to 11:27~32).
Bo5 hap8-gi5 e5, chiu7-si7 sin3-chia2 chai-iaN2 u7 choe7, na7-si7 bo5 jin7-choe7. Lan2 tioh8 jin7-choe7 tu5-khi3 phaiN2-tai7, tit-tioh8 Chu2 e5 po2-huih soe2 chheng-khi3 kap sia3-bian2, lan2 chiah thang siu7 Seng3-chhan. Siong7-te3 hoan-hu3 sin3-chia2 tioh8 ka-ki7 seng2-chhat hun-piat8, na7 m7 an2-ni choe3, chiu7-si7 tui3 lim-chiah8 ka-ki7 chhu2 sim2-phoaN3, i3-su3 chiu7-si7 beh siu7 chek-hoat8.
Ui7-tioh8 an2-ni, Siong7-te3 kong2, I e5 kiaN2-ji5 u7 choe7-choe7 lang5 soe-lan2 koh phoa3-piN7, si2 e5 ia7 bo5 chio2. Goa2 bo5 kong2 sou2 u7 e5 phoa3-piN7, long2 si7 tui3 choe7-ok lai5, chong2-si7 kiam2-chhai2 u7 choe7-choe7 e5 soe-lan2 kap phoa3-piN7, si7 tui3 m7 jin7-choe7 lai5 in2-khi2 e5; kiam2-chhai2 li2 sit-giap8 ia7-si7 an2-ni. In-ui7 Siong7-te3 eng7 chiah-e5 khian5-keng3 teh tui3-hu3, sim2-phoaN3 kap chek-hoat8 li2, I ai3 in2-chhoa7 li2 to3-tng2 koh chit8 pai2 kap I kau-poe5; li2 na7 iau2-ku2 bo5 beh jin7-choe7, bo5 eng5-kng I, koh hou7 I kian3-siau3, I kiam2-chhai2 beh chhu2 li2 e5 siN3-mia7.
Siong7-te3 u7 ka7 lan2 kong2, lan2 na7 ka-ki7 sim2-mng7, chiu7 bo5 siu7 sim2-phoaN3. OaN7 oe7 lai5 kong2, lan2 na7 beh jin7-choe7, hoan2-hoe2, tit-tioh8 I e5 sia3-bian2, I chiu7 bo5 beh keng2-kai3 lan2. TaN Siong7-te3 koh ka7 lan2 kong2 chin beng5, I sim2-phoaN3 lan2 e5 si5, chiu7 chek-hoat8 lan2, in-ui7 lan2 si7 I e5 kiaN2-ji5, I m7-ai3 lan2 kap se3-kan lang5 saN-kap siu7 teng7-choe7. Ki3-jian5 choe3 I e5 kiaN2-ji5, I chiu7 beh an2-ni khoan2-thai7 lan2, lan2 tioh8 jim2-siu7 Siong7-te3 e5 keng2-kai3. Li2 e5 siu7-khou2, kiam2-chhai2 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 sim2-phoaN3, chek-hoat8, chi2-u7 jin7-choe7, kap Siong7-te3 ho5-ho2 chiah bian2 siu7 I keng2-kai3.
6. Kiann5 Ti7 Kng-beng5, Tak8-jit8 Tit-tioh8 Chheng-khi3.
¡§Tok8-tok8 lan2 na7 kiaN5 ti7 kng-beng5, chhin-chhiuN7 I tiam3-ti7 kng-beng5, chiu7 lan2 saN-kap kau-poe5, ia7 I e5 KiaN2 Ia5-sou e5 huih soe2-tu5 lan2 long2-chong2 e5 choe7¡¨ (I Iok-han7 1:7). Lan2 tioh8 sun7-hok8 Chu2, li7-khui it-chhe3 lan2 sou2 chai e5 put-gi7 kap choe7-ok, chiau3 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3 lai5 oah8. An2-ni chiah oe7 thang kiaN5 ti7 kng-beng5. Lan2 na7 hoan7 choe7, chiu7 bo5 kiaN5 ti7 kng-beng5, in-ui7 lan2 chai, choe7 si7 m7-tioh8, put-gi7. lang5 na7 kiaN5 ti7 kng-beng5, chiu7 jit8-jit8 tui3 i e5 choe7 tit-tioh8 soe2-chheng.
